---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="首页">
  <section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        欢迎来到
        <span class="text-[#f3d230]">柴火创客学院</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        培养创新思维，激发动手能力，让每个孩子都能成为未来的创造者
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/courses"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-white bg-[#d84144] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#c13538] transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          探索课程
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 bg-[#f3d230] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#e5c420] transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          预约体验
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
